description_data.value: ** RESERVED ** This candidate has been reserved by an organization or individual that will use it when announcing a new security problem. When the candidate has been publicized, the details for this candidate will be provided.

descriptions.value: An issue was discovered on WyreStorm Apollo VX20 devices before 1.3.58. The TELNET service prompts for a password only after a valid username is entered, which might make it easier for remote attackers to enumerate user accounts.

Se descubrió un problema en dispositivos WyreStorm Apollo VX20 anteriores a la versión 1.3.58. El servicio TELNET solicita una contraseña sólo después de introducir un nombre de usuario válido, lo que podría facilitar a atacantes remotos la enumeración de cuentas de usuario.
